2.6.41.name: wordpress/wp-survey
2.6.41.description:
This plugin is only supported on PHP 5.2 or greater.

SurveyMe is an easy to use and easy to modify survey tool for WordPress. Written to be easy to use to none coders.

If you are having trouble and cannot find the answers in the FAQ you can post your support questions to the WordPress Support Forum

If you find SurveyMe useful please rate it at wordpress.org and please consider making a donation to help us set aside more hours to maintain SurveyMe

SurveyMe is written by dcoda

You can check out our other plugins here

If you require a custom plugin you can contact us
